site_name: Site of Perotti House and Coomer House

protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of Perotti House and Coomer House and redevelopment of the site excluding Barton House as erection of buildings between 4 and 7 storeys (Wandsworth Bridge Rd frontage) and 2 to 7 storeys (Townmead Rd frontage), a terrace of 2 storey properties (De Morgan Rd frontage) and a single storey building providing a total of 158 res units, retail floorspace, doctors surgeries and a replacement nursery/tenants hall together with the formation of a ball games court (within the site) and a central area of communal open space, related landscaping, car parking (101 spaces) and servicing
site_number: Site of Perotti House and Coomer House
